sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ContentScript as Content Script
    participant Background as Background SW
    participant Offscreen as Offscreen Document
    participant IDB as IndexedDB

    User->>ContentScript: Types prompt and sends (click/Ctrl+Enter)
    ContentScript->>ContentScript: Extract prompt text
    ContentScript->>Background: { action: "storePrompt", text, source }
    Background->>Offscreen: { action: "embedAndStore", text, source }
    Offscreen->>Offscreen: Embed text (MiniLM-L6-v2) -> 384-dim vector
    Offscreen->>IDB: Save { text, embedding, source, timestamp }
    Offscreen-->>Background: { success: true }
    Background-->>ContentScript: ack